'''圣约翰伍德'''（St John's Wood）位于伦敦西北部[[西敏市|西敏市]]，[[摄政公园|摄政公园]]西北侧，[[查令十字|查令十字]]西北4公里。历史上为[[圣约翰骑士团|圣约翰骑士团]]的领地<ref name="SJWS">The St. John's Wood Society. [http://www.stjohnswood.org.uk/sjw/index.html 圣约翰伍德的历史] {{Wayback|url=http://www.stjohnswood.org.uk/sjw/index.html |date=20110828161935 }}. 2011-01-24</ref>。

这是一个非常富裕的社区<ref>{{cite web |last=Sherwood |first=Bob |url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/98f279f2-4294-11df-91d6-00144feabdc0.html#axzz2SMGwBIPC |title=Affluent enclave sitting on political front line |work=Financial Times |date=2010-04-07 |accessdate=2014-10-01 |archive-date=2014-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814042802/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/98f279f2-4294-11df-91d6-00144feabdc0.html#axzz2SMGwBIPC |dead-url=no }}</ref>，根据[[福布斯|福布斯]]杂志的排名，2007年的平均房价在伦敦排名第5位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/2007/12/11/postcodes-uk-expensive-forbeslife-cx_po_1212realestatelondon_slide_6.html |title=In Pictures: London's Most Expensive Postcodes |work=Forbes |accessdate=2014-10-01 |archive-date=2014-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007010918/http://www.forbes.com/2007/12/11/postcodes-uk-expensive-forbeslife-cx_po_1212realestatelondon_slide_6.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年，圣约翰伍德的房价再度攀升。

